text: Manav Thakkar is an Indian table-tennis player. He was a part of the Indian team for the India at the 2018 Asian Games. Manav Thakkar was born in Rajkot,Gujarat. Thakkar currently holds the number 1 position in ITTF World Under-21 Men Singles Rankings. == References == Category:Indian male table tennis players Category:Living people Category:Year of birth missing (living people)
